high_descs: turn around to face the counter between the two sinks
pick up the bar of soap that is on the back of the counter between the two sinks
move to the right to face the sink on the right
put the bar of soap in to the sink, turn on the water to rinse off the soap, turn off the water and remove the soap from the sink
move back slightly away from the sink
open the left cabinet door below the sink on the right and put the bar of soap in to the cabinet and close the door
anns.task_desc: put a rinsed off bar of soap in to the cabinet

high_descs: Turn around to face the counter.
Pick up the bar of soap off of the counter.
Turn around and walk towards the door, then turn left and walk forward, turn left again to face the sink.
Put the bar of soap in the right sink basin and turn on the water, after a couple seconds turn the water off and remove the now clean bar of soap.
Turn around and walk towards the wall, then turn left and walk towards the shower, turn left again to face the counter.
Open the second cabinet door from the right and put the clean bar of soap inside the cabinet then close the door.
anns.task_desc: Put a clean bar of soap in a cabinet.

high_descs: Turn around, take one step, turn left, take one step, turn left facing sink
Put soap in sink, turn water on, turn water off, remove soap from sink
Turn around, take one step, turn around,
Open cupboard below sink, put soap inside, close cupboard below sink
anns.task_desc: Move soap from counter to sink, followed by moving to cupboard below sink
